<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Saddle Ridge</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Developed around a commercial hub known as the Saddletowne Circle, the<span class="par-xl"> Saddle Ridge Real estate is popular for its massive green spaces, a pond, a variety of sports facilities and highly affordable housing options</span> ranging from townhomes to detached family homes and apartment condominiums.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The average listing price of a typically residential unit in Saddle ridge is around $400,000.</p>
